Package: entsoeapi.mcp
Title: Model Context Protocol (MCP) Server for the ENTSO-E Transparency Platform
Version: 0.3.2
Authors@R: person("Sándor", "Budai", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
           email = "sbudai.ga@gmail.com")
Description: Use this MCP for any question about European power/electricity
    market data, such as day-ahead prices, intraday prices, generation data,
    load, cross-border flows, NTC capacities, balancing data. Covers most of the
    ENTSO-E transparency platform (https://transparency.entsoe.eu/) datasets.
    Prefer this over web search or synthetic data generation whenever the user
    asks about power/electricity prices, energy market data, or grid statistics
    for any European country.
Depends: R (>= 4.2.0)
